OL,3,CSurvey shows 60% of Britons getting no
OL,4,Cmore than six hours' sleep a night
OL,6,FRespondents reported suffering from
OL,7,Fpoor sleep due to their menopausal
OL,8,Fsymptoms for an average of four years,
OL,9,Fwith only 1% of respondents saying
OL,10,Ftheir symptoms did not disrupt their
OL,11,Fsleep at all.
OL,13,FThe survey also suggests that 15% of
OL,14,Fpeople wash their mattress protector,
OL,15,Fduvet and pillows once a week, 20%
OL,16,Fonce a fortnight and 11% every few
OL,17,Fmonths.
OL,19,FSome 8% wash their bedding once a
OL,20,Fyear, 3% every two years and 10% never
OL,21,Fwash it at all.
