OL,3,CSurvey shows 60% of Britons getting no
OL,4,Cmore than six hours' sleep a night
OL,6,FWoolroom managing director Chris
OL,7,FTattersall said: "By creating the
OL,8,FClean Sleep Report, we wanted to
OL,9,Funderstand the nation's attitude
OL,10,Ftowards sleep and their awareness of
OL,11,Fthe sleep environment's impact on our
OL,12,Fhealth and planet.
OL,14,F"What has emerged from the survey
OL,15,Ffindings is that there is a clear
OL,16,Fdisconnect between people's attitude
OL,17,Ftowards sleep and the amount and
OL,18,Fquality they're actually getting.
